                "text":"Power Plant Worker:",
                "size":20,
                "color":"#CDCDB4"
            },
            {
                "text":"Can instantly construct '[Power Plant]'",
                "size":18
            },
            {
                "text":"e.g. [Coal-fired Plant], [Oil-fired Plant], [Nuclear Fission Plant], [Nuclear Fusion Plant], [Solar Plant], [Wind Plant], [Geothermal Plant], [Tidal Plant]",
